As our heroes travel onward, a new challenge awaits them,
and so do many new and unusual Pokemon.
-Why is it tied up like that?
You mean that someone just left it here alone?
It has the potential to evolve into any one of three different Pokemon.
I do not think you should.
That is the place at the foot of Evolution Mountain.
Eevee evolves into one of three Pokemon,
depending on what stone is used on it.
Using a fire stone will yield Flareon, the flame Pokemon.
A water stone yields Vaporeon, the bubble jet Pokemon.
A thunder stone yields Jolteon, the lighting Pokemon.
Huh, I would love a Vaporeon.
All you ever think about is water Pokemon.

We have got our star, now we can go on with the show.
-Uh, then why was it tied up?

Why did you bring it back?

Do you really think you can win your first battle

The key to a first victory is evolution.

A water stone will make it a Vaporeon.

A fire stone will make it a Flareon.

Flareon is the strongest evolutionary choice of all.
My Jolteon is the strongest of all.
Too bad you are the only one who thinks so.
Heh, Mikey, I am sure you will make the right choice

That is a lot of pressure to put on the little guy.
Hey, give the kid a break, will you?
Is not he a little young to battle?
We are throwing this party just for him and his Eevee.
You should know you have to start training early if you want to become a master.
Yeah, one of these days, you will turn that Pikachu into a Raichu will not you?
Wow, water stones, and thunder and fire.
You really have collected a lot of them.
That is what our town's known for.
But you cannot mine them all the time.
That is a special edition of the Pokemon Friend.
Yeah, we used it to plan today's special evolution party.

Then why do not you just make it evolve?

Evolution is what Pokemon are all about.
It is been a while, has not it?
It does not seem like you really want to make Eevee evolve, do you, Mikey?
My brothers do not care about anything but battling Pokemon.
I was trying to hide Eevee from them, just for today.
Then nobody could force me to make it evolve at the party.
But Eevee looked very, very lonely out there.
I was going to go get it later.
I do not care if Eevee evolves or not.
I just want it to be my best friend.

You were just running away from your problems.
If you do not want Eevee to evolve, tell your brothers how you feel.
That is your responsibility as a trainer.
But, hey, I am not your mother or anything.
If you had not claimed Eevee,
I was going to keep it and change it into Vaporeon myself.
I wonder what they are saying.

-You just do not get it, do you?
We just do not evolve our Pokemon that way.
You like your way of evolving, and we like ours.
That is the way to tell them, Brock.

Have you decided on Eevee's evolution yet?
-Come right out and tell him, Mike.

To unite all peoples within our nation...
To denounce the evils of truth and love...

All the food is gone too!
Team Rocket took the stones, and they took the food too.
-Why could not they take you too?
That was easier than taking candy from a baby.
Candy and cold cuts and Pokemon too.
Ah, nothing tastes better than a victory meal.
We have gotten beaten so many times, I would forgotten what victory tasted like.
I do not ever want you to call us losers again.
From now on, we will be known as Team Rocket, champions of the world.
Why do not you two dry up?
It is time make that little one evolve.

That is why we need it to be a Jolteon.

-Weezing, hit it with a sludge attack!
Vaporeon, use your acid armor and fight back!
Do not let them get away!
So you thought you had us beat, did you?
We are the champion Team Rocket.
-We cannot lose this battle to them.
-Especially on our first day as champions.
There is something different about Team Rocket.
-It is time to finish them off.
It is time for our first real battle!
What is this, a stuffed animal?
It looks like champion Team Rocket...
Winning your first battle by yourself, that is incredible.

You always said you did not want to battle, but you did great.
I just wanted to help everybody out.
I have decided to become an Eevee trainer.
Well, Mikey, if that is what you want to do, then do it.
If you felt that way about it, you should have told us sooner.
Now we really are the four Eevee brothers.
Hey, guys, let us make this party a celebration of Eevee's first victory.
I wanted to thank you for helping me.
I am sure you will become a great Eevee trainer.

You could pass for my brother.
